{"tid":468563,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"〔震驚〕每日150人，六個月就填滿一條華富邨","createTime":"2017-11-14T13:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T07:35:41.000Z","uid":77905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1862c7b7251028eb94e4a6ab8fd66e00e1446800","tid":468563,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"一條新公屋邨由構思到入伙要四至五年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先要不斷搵地 <br />\n起近居民又會批評插針 又要咨詢區議員<br />\n已發展地區搵唔到就要填海 又要發展郊野公園 <br />\n到搵到有地  就要委聘顧問進行發展研究<br />\n評估土地規劃、社區設施以同交通需求對附近交通影響幾大<br />\n之後又要設計同興建 睇要有咩規劃同設計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞咁多嘢<br />\n每日150人<br />\n六個月就填滿條邨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add8dcda67c7ac0efff3559a8ee1b4b8b63c7936","tid":468563,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知阿媽係女人咩<br />\n垃圾政府唔停150<br />\n可以點?"},{"pid":"560968d19107e6ea6327e5ec9a10e76de2e0d394","tid":468563,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08ddec6dda762323c3fb7e04c1d8227d0e2b4152","tid":468563,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"要同排緊公屋的港人宣傳"},{"pid":"06c9ebd97f9b6a21f2304ffa8ad1d25716b501ed","tid":468563,"uid":14298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"其實班議員有無得動議取消每日150人"},{"pid":"612a6c5fb48898f6d09f7824cc65f4f9f9818564","tid":468563,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c9ebd97f9b6a21f2304ffa8ad1d25716b501ed","tid":468563,"uid":14298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"其實班議員有無得動議取消每日150人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:35:41.000Z","msg":"無議員敢出聲"}]}